final case class ReplicatedEntity(name: String = "", entityType: String = "", replicatedData: ReplicatedData = kalix.component.ReplicatedEntity.ReplicatedData.Empty, unknownFields: UnknownFieldSet = _root_.scalapb.UnknownFieldSet.empty) extends GeneratedMessage with Updatable[ReplicatedEntity] with Product with Serializable
